name: Sun and her daughters - The Collection
description:
This is the complete 13-piece song cycle inspired by planetary objects in our solar system. These were all composed as part of commission for @johnowhitaker. All were performed on the Roland JDxi except Saturn, Uranus, and Neptune which were composed in GarageBand on the iPad. Album art was created using VQGAN-CLIP.

01 00:00 Mercury, arise! 
02 01:41 Venus awaits 
03 02:57 Earth, alone
04 04:58 Mars affair 
05 07:43 Ceres ardent 
06 08:32 Jupiter attired 
07 09:56 Saturn asks 
08 11:16 Uranus above  
09 11:53 Neptune, alas!  
10 12:52 Pluto awry 
11 14:02 Eris alive 
12 14:38 Makemake after 
13 16:04 Haumea, at last!
